{"id":603144031,"lang":"cpp","lang_name":"C++","time":"1 year, 8 months","timestamp":1639745669,"status":11,"status_display":"Wrong Answer","runtime":"N/A","url":"/submissions/detail/603144031/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Longest Substring Without Repeating Characters","memory":"N/A","code":"class Solution {\npublic:\n    \n    int lengthOfLongestSubstring(string s) {\n        int n = s.size();\n        unordered_map<char,int> set;\n        int m = 0;\n        int i = 0;\n        for(int j = 0; j < n; ++j){\n            if(set.count(s[j])){\n                i = max(i, set[s[j] +1]);\n            }\n            set[s[j]] = j;\n            m = max(m, j-i);\n        }\n        return m;\n    }\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"longest-substring-without-repeating-characters","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
